videos.description: JT Daniels finds Tyler Vaughns on the out route, who then carries it in for a 2-yard touchdown to put USC on the board.
videos.headline: Daniels hits Vaughns for 2-yard TD

videos.description: Aca'Cedric Ware follows his blockers then erupts for a 44-yard gain to set up USC for a 1st-and-goal.
videos.headline: Ware bursts for a 44-yard gain

videos.description: Cal QB Chase Garbers tucks it, breaks tackles and bursts to the 1-yard line for a 82 yard gain, but it is called back after a holding call.
videos.headline: Cal holding call erases 82-yard play

videos.description: JT Daniels threads the needle and hits a wide-open Tyler Vaughns for a 23-yard touchdown to extend USC's lead to 14-0.
videos.headline: Daniels connects with Vaughns for 23-yard TD

videos.description: USC QB JT Daniels calls for the ball, but the snap is high and goes into the end zone where Daniels recovers for a Cal safety.
videos.headline: High snap leads to Cal safety

videos.description: Cal Vic Wharton III beats his man in the slot and connects with Chase Garbers for a 29-yard touchdown pass to cut USC's lead to 14-9.
videos.headline: Garbers floats one up to Wharton for 29-yard TD

videos.description: USC QB JT Daniels rips a pass to the slot receiver, but is picked off by Cal's Traveon Beck to put Cal on USC's 40-yard line.
videos.headline: Beck's interception put Cal in great field position

videos.description: Cal QB Chase Garber keeps the ball, breaks a couple of tackles and runs in a 5-yard touchdown to give Cal a 15-14 lead.
videos.headline: Garbers punches in 5-yard TD

videos.description: On 3rd-and-6 with 2:40 to go, Cal QB Chase Garbers fakes the handoff and rolls out the pocket to get the first down and seal the win, but comes up short.
videos.headline: Cal tries fake to seal win over USC
